Modifications by the Wizard authors on top of Stockfish 15.1:
  - Engine identity / branding (UCI `id name` / `id author`).
  - Integrated Polyglot opening-book support (book probing in the UCI
    search loop; original book-reader implementation).
  - Bullet-oriented time-management configuration and latency tuning
    for online (Lichess) play.
  - NNUE integration verification tooling and the deployment pipeline
    (Docker / lichess-bot).

The NNUE evaluation network (nn-ad9b42354671.nnue) is the Stockfish 15.1
default network, distributed under GPL-3 as part of Stockfish.

